name: CHIMOON
description: This moon cat named "Chimoon" is a form of my pride for the island I live in because it still has one species that is threatened with extinction, namely the "Javanese leopard" due to conflicts between humans and animals in the wild. I have hope that the conservation carried out by the local community can have a positive impact on the life of this rare animal in the long term. Here I hope that this community can access and collect for a form of support for the survival of endangered animals
